Privacy Policy
Craox Technologies LLP built the
HOME PLANNER APP
as a Freemium app. This SERVICE is provided by
Craox Technologies LLP
at no cost and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our Service.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, which is accessible at
HOME PLANNER
unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.
What Data We Collect and Why
We collect information you provide and some data automatically when you use our services. This helps us deliver a better experience and improve our services. Below is a summary of what we collect and why:
1. Personal Information You Provide
We collect the information you willingly share, such as:
Name and Email Address: Used for registration, communication, and account management.
Photos and Camera Access: If you upload photos, these are analyzed to provide personalized recommendations. This feature is essential to our app's functionality. Your photos are used solely for this purpose and are not shared without consent.
You can update this information as needed to keep it accurate.
2. Application Data
If you use our app, we may request access to certain features:
Mobile Device Access: Permissions for features like the camera photo are needed to use core functionalities. You can adjust these permissions anytime in your device settings.
Push Notifications: Notifications related to your account or app features may be sent. You can disable these in your device settings.
Photos and Camera Use: These are used exclusively for analyzing and creating personalized recommendations.
3. Automatically Collected Information
When you use our services, we collect non-identifiable technical data to enhance performance, security, and analytics:
Log and Usage Data: Includes IP address, browser type, device info, and usage patterns (e.g., visited pages and features used). This helps us maintain and improve the service.
Device Data: Includes details about your device, such as model, operating system, browser type, and location. This ensures optimal compatibility and performance.
Why We Collect This Data
We use this data to:
Provide and enhance our app's core functionalities.
Improve your experience by offering personalized recommendations.
Ensure security and proper app operation.
Generate analytics to optimize and expand our services.
The app does use third party services that may collect information used to identify you.
Link to privacy policy of third party service providers used by the app.
